content_html: Kathmandu, Sept 16: Newly appointed Prime Minister Sushila Karki visited the Tilganga Eye Hospital today for a regular eye examination. PM Karki reached Tilganga today and had a regular eye checkup, the Prime Minister's Secretariat said. Senior Ophthalmologist Dr Sanduk Ruit examined the Prime Minister's eyes
